name: Aqsa Kausar
bio: Tuning my hyper-parameters everyday to dive deeper into the foray of deep learning.
photoURL: Aqsa is a curious Machine Learning Engineer who is passionate about technology, learning new things and sharing ideas with others. As an ML Engineer she has hands-on experience with a diverse set of projects ranging from footfall forecasting to cataract detection. She has also worked on projects related to augmented reality, object detection and recommender systems.
